Description: convert from GLFW/GLEW/BASS to SDL2/SDL2_mixer/libepoxy
 Replace GLFW with SDL2 for window management and input handling.
 Replace GLEW with libepoxy for OpenGL extension loading (Wayland/EGL compatible).
 Replace BASS with SDL2_mixer for audio playback.
 This enables native Wayland support since libepoxy transparently uses EGL or GLX.
Generated-by: Claude Sonnet 4.6
Reviewed-by: Nicolas HOUDELOT <nicolas@demosdebs.org>
Applied-Upstream: no
